    "New PyTorch dynamo-based ONNX exporter required the 'onnxscript' package - installed separately (same issue the Kaggle GPU notebook hit).",
    "PyTorch's dynamo ONNX exporter prints a unicode checkmark character during export, which crashed on Windows' default cp1252 console encoding (UnicodeEncodeError). Resolved by setting PYTHONIOENCODING=utf-8 and PYTHONUTF8=1 before running the export script."
